profile:
LALONDE HOME & DESIGN CENTRE
​
We are a local company located in Fort McMurray Alberta, specializing in the design and installation of cabinets and countertops.  If you are looking to remodel or build your dream kitchen, look no further! 

We have over 25 years of experience in the field. We also supply and install masonry stone and siding. including outdoor kitchens. We do the full scope of work for drywall including attic blowing (insulation), texture ceiling application and repairs. 

​Lalonde Home & Design Centre is your one stop shop in Fort McMurray Alberta.
project_minimum: No job is too small or big

We strive to provide the best service possible for our clients. We believe in building a relationship, because to us you aren't just a number. We want to make sure you get the best product and service possible.



We provide a free evaluation with our findings as well as photos to provide to your insurance company to help you get what you need.



We have two mobile rigs running at all times and are willing to travel, so don't be afraid to ask!
